The Great Chelsea Garden Challenge - Series 1, Episode 4




Conceptual Gardens

Only four designers remain and this time they have come to Painswick Rocco Garden in the heart of the Cotswolds. They must create conceptual gardens which will showcase their creativity and impress judges James Alexander-Sinclair and Ann-Marie Powell.




Original Air Date: 13-May-2015
